response.overview: "All I've Got"- Jason Manning leads the cast in this dramatic adventure based on the true life and music of "Gary Wey". Full of life, love, and the harsh reality of pursuing a Rock & Roll lifestyle in the early 1970's. "All I've Got" takes you on a passionate journey through Gary's life that will leave you wanting more! "All I've Got" features a sound track packed full of awe inspiring never heard before "classics". Written and Directed by Jason Manning. Starring- Jason Manning, Jamielee Eldridge, Rob Diamond, and Marlys Miller-Fladeland.
response.title: aLL i'Ve goT
